item.title: Raphael Warnock biograph
item.description: Senator Raphael Warnock Biograph Senator Raphael Gamaliel Warnock is an American politician and pastor. He is serving as a junior U.S. Senator from Georgia under the Democrats since 2021. He is a senior pastor of the Ebenezer Baptist Church in Atlanta, Georgia. Warnock was born in Savannah, Georgia, on July 23, 1969. He was born to a war veteran dad where he grew up to learn auto mechanic works. He also learned to weld and later opened a junk car restoration business.
